		<h1 class="the_title">Social program</h1>

				<section class="entry">
			
			<p>It is a good tradition that during the ISOTT meeting in the evening the participants get the opportunity to have fruitful discussions in a relaxed atmosphere. For this reason we will have three evening events during the meeting:</p>
<p>We visit a local microbrewery in Halle („Hallesches Brauhaus“). You can taste different beer specialities and traditional food in a rustic environment close to the brewing copper.<samp></samp></p>
<p><a href="https://isott2017.org/files/2017/04/Saline1.jpg"><img class="wp-image-321 alignleft" src="https://isott2017.org/files/2017/04/Saline1-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="255" height="191" srcset="http://isott2017.org/files/2017/04/Saline1-300x225.jpg 300w, http://isott2017.org/files/2017/04/Saline1-150x113.jpg 150w, http://isott2017.org/files/2017/04/Saline1.jpg 550w" sizes="(max-width: 255px) 100vw, 255px"></a></p>
<p>We then learn in the saline museum of how Halle became a prosperous city by making salt. Of course there will be plenty to eat and drink.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
